name: Samsung I9190 Galaxy S4 Mini  **BRAND NEW**
description:
Android 4.2 Jelly Bean operating system
Along with a Qualcomm MSM8930 Snapdragon 400 chipset allows you to stay connected and productive on the go.
3G speed
Offers quick and easy connection speeds. Wi-Fi hotspot capability provides a wireless Web connection for compatible devices.
Wi-Fi 802.11a/b/g/n network
For Internet capability on the go.
Bluetooth 4.0 technology with A2DP + LE + EDR
Allows simple wireless communication with a Bluetooth-enabled device.
Super AMOLED capacitive touch screen
With 16M colors offers clear viewing and easy navigation of content.
microSD card slot
Makes it simple to expand storage (card not included).
8.0MP camera
With touch focus, an LED flash and face detection makes it easy to snap stunning photos. Geotagging lets you add location information to your shots.
MP3 player
Allows you to enjoy your favorite tunes while on the go.
Hands-free speakerphone
Lets you talk while driving.
Sensors
Include accelerometer, gyro, proximity and compass for versatile use.
* Unlocked cell phones are compatible with GSM carriers, including AT&T and T-Mobile; also compatible with GSM SIM cards, including H20 and NET10.
* Phone will not work with Sprint, Verizon, Boost Mobile, Virgin Mobile or any other CDMA carriers. Please contact your carrier prior to purchasing to confirm your carrier will support voice and data on this unlocked GSM device.

name: Apple iPhone 5s      **BRAND NEW**
description:
The highly advanced iPhone 5s features the A7 chip with 64-bit architecture, the Touch ID fingerprint sensor, a new 8MP iSight camera, a new FaceTime HD camera, ultrafast LTE wireless, iOS 7, and iCloud. Yet it's as thin and light as ever.
Product Features

4-inch Retina display
A7 chip with M7 motion coprocessor
Touch ID fingerprint sensor
New 8MP iSight camera with True Tone flash
1080p HD video recording
FaceTime HD camera
Ultrafast LTE wireless

Over 900,000 apps on the App Store

name: Samsung Galaxy Note 10.1 N8000 **BRAND NEW**
description:
Android 4.0 Ice Cream Sandwich operating system
Along with a 1.4GHz quad-core processor allows you to stay connected and productive on the go.
Built-in 802.11a/b/g/n wireless LAN
Connect to the Internet without wires.
2GB memory
For multitasking power.
10.1" TFT touch-screen display
With WXGA (1280 x 800) resolution showcases movies and games in stunning clarity. S Pen technology lets you draw, annotate and create handwritten notes with ease.
16GB on-board eMMC memory
Provides plenty of space for your photos, music, movies and more.
Built-in 1.9MP front-facing webcam
Makes it easy to video chat with family and friends. The rear-facing 5.0MP camera with autofocus and power LED flash allows you to capture high-quality images.
microSD card slot
Supports cards up to 32GB for storing or transferring media (card not included).
Bluetooth 4.0 (LE)
Easily link with other Bluetooth-enabled devices, such as a mobile phone or MP3 player.
Weighs only 1.3 lbs. and measures just 0.4" thin
For lightweight portability.
Preloaded apps
Include Google Play, Google Talk, Netflix, YouTube and more.
